BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF OHIO:
Section 1. That section 5501.84 of the Revised Code be 5
enacted to read as follows: 6
Sec. 5501.84. (A) As used in this section : 7
(1) "Foreign adversary" means 8
a country listed on the registry published by the 9
secretary of state under division (C) of this section. 10
(2) "Public entity" means the state and all political 11
subdivisions of the state, including all boards, authorities, 12
commissions, agencies, committees, councils, state colleges or 13
universities, and other state entities created by the Ohio 14
Constitution or the Revised Code. 15
(3) "Small unmanned aircraft system" means a powered, 16
aerial vehicle to which all of the following apply: 17
(a) The vehicle does not carry a human operator and is 18

